    {
      "title": "WARGEAR OPTIONS",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "Up to 4 Devastator Marines can each have their boltgun replaced with one of the following:",
          "items": [
            "1 grav-cannon",
            "1 heavy bolter",
            "1 lascannon",
            "1 missile launcher",
            "1 multi-melta",
            "1 plasma cannon"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "option_group",
          "label": "The Devastator Sergeant\u2019s bolt pistol and boltgun can be replaced with two different weapons from the following list:*",
          "items": [
            "1 Astartes chain sword",
            "1 bolt pistol",
            "1 boltgun",
            "1 combi-weapon",
            "1 grav-pistol",
            "1 plasma pistol",
            "1 power fist",
            "1 power weapon",
            "1 thunder hammer"
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "text": "* This model can only be equipped with two ranged weapons if one of them is a Pistol (and it can only have one Pistol)"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "ABILITIES",
      "entries": [
        {
          "type": "tagged_list",
          "label": "FACTION",
          "items": [
            "Oath of Moment Signum: Each time this unit Remains Stationary , until the start of your next Movement phase , ranged weapons equipped by models in this unit have the [IGNORES COVER] ability. Armorium Cherub: Once per battle, after making a Hit roll for a model in this unit, you can change that roll to an unmodified 6. Designer\u2019s Note: Place an Armorium Cherub token next to the unit, removing it once this ability has been used."
